Original Problem: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bridge_and_torch_problem
Solution by Professor Roland Backhouse: www.cs.nott.ac.uk/~rcb/MPC/GeneralTorchProblem.ps

Installation: 
1) You will need WxHaskell installed: http://www.haskell.org/haskellwiki/WxHaskell

2) Follow these steps to create a stand-alone application:
> cd General-Capcity-C-Torch-Problem-Solver/
> ghc -package wx -o TorchSolver TorchSolver.hs
> /usr/local/wxhaskell/bin/macosx-app -v TorchSolver
> open TorchSolver.app